snippet.title: DONKEY.SMS : A Master System homebrew game inspired by DONKEY.BAS
snippet.description:
This is a homebrew game for Master System consoles inspired by the game DONKEY.BAS that shipped with MS-DOS in 1981!

(This footage was recorded with the autopilot cheat enabled, this is why it looks so easy.)

For more information about this homebrew game, please visit the project page:
https://www.raphnet.net/programmation/donkey/index_en.php
